{"type": "article", "id": 57094, "title": "百叶窗还能做成家具？搭配玻璃亚克力效果不错｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-10-08T22:51:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 53277, "name": "1/plinth"}, {"id": 24532, "name": "Prepd"}, {"id": 53278, "name": "umindesign"}, {"id": 47967, "name": "Republic of Fritz Hansen"}, {"id": 40160, "name": "Visibility"}, {"id": 44901, "name": "Jaime Hayon"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 72, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181008215050aHMbVfDkpXLiCKIq.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Louver by 1/plinth</h3><p>首尔设计工作室 1/plinth 近日推出了名为 Louver 的系列作品，包括橱柜、置物架、书桌、桌子、矮桌、座椅、坐凳以及长椅等 8 款产品，是设计者通过独特视角对现有工业材料加以利用的结果。</p><p>Louver 全部采用铝制百叶窗和铝制挤压框架制作而成，突出展示了材料未经处理的独特美感以及微妙的粗糙感。</p><p>Louver 系列家具的基础结构是一个铝制框架系统，具有多功能特性，可以利用多种模具直接挤压再修剪至所需长度。不仅如此，框架还无需焊接，仅需使用多种硬件便能按照多种不同方式进行组装。在基础框架上方，表面充满三种不同元素：百叶窗、钢化玻璃以及半透明亚克力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215130t6HNF4RPfBmqcusI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215133zk8TtyRo3LSGEvZg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215130vmSW6fPK94wVnAgL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215130t9TGcFN4LC0wXSeh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215134kzNGEUR3AajXKuJs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215134frymT8PXAzLDdGxg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215134NagrGJ0kSH3hmAQv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.661369\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://1plinth.com/projects\" rel=\"nofollow\">1/plinth</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Prepd Colors - The World's Best Lunchbox by Prepd</h3><p>午餐是一天中最重要的一餐，但往往因为日常繁忙而囫囵吞枣，或随便吃吃。加上越来越多的饮食安全问题、越来越贵的物价，带便当逐渐成为新趋势。</p><p>这是 Prepd Pack 便当盒的升级版本，Prepd Colors 可轻松拆卸，并且拥有多种配置方式，满足每个人的日常与喜好需求。更重要的是，便当盒是由安全、完全防漏的材料制成。此外，它还配有专属 App，精心规划，简化你准备午餐的时间与精力，甚至还提供购物清单，让用户知道需要购买哪些食材。</p><p>与便当盒搭配的，还有一款便当包，是一层优质织物衬里氯丁橡胶，这是一种柔韧、耐热和耐磨的材料，一般用于制作潜水服，起到保温功能。目前，Prepd Colors 在众筹网站 Kickstarter 上的售价为 19 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/prepd/prepd-colors\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215514syF3YrDnMwHNzECu.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.911765\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215514BgdwDCI4FSL0NfR9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.911765\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810082155156nbeaNO8vpFXyk5r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.847059\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215513cnArQDa6gx4ohCZO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.464706\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810082155154zrqcbQhvx73GnAa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.913235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Square Pin Boards by umindesign</h3><p>umin design 的新作是一块方形图钉板。错视的方形由两种材质结合。面料部分是可以固定图钉的区域，金属部分则可以磁吸，满足用户收集多样的素材。</p><p>设计团队希望这一块板不是常规图钉板的材料和外形，它甚至直接还可以作为家里或者是工作室墙面的装饰物。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=u1349cd8i1q\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215734f3j1o0KSn7iZ4kTJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810082157342I8V3HhECw1GoYWL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215735DAViwLCOJNG8340r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.678889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215735XHUztx7hMnprkFuq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.430000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215734FOguREcVabB3vrNz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.208571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215735KeyJBqmxzMaQ9Fr6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.404286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.umindesign.com/a/hualang_chanpin/39.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">umindesign</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Plenum by Jaime Hayon for Republic of Fritz Hansen</h3><p>丹麦顶级家居品牌 Republic of Fritz Hansen 最近推出了一个全新的高靠背沙发系列 Plenum，出自西班牙鬼才设计师 Jaime Hayon 之手。Plenum 系列是为适应不断变化的现代办公空间设计，包括单人、双人和三人座沙发，同时配备电源插口、USB 插口以及一体式或分离式桌子。</p><p>柔软的形态、有机的曲线以及充满趣味的配色，是 Plenum 系列的特征，也将其与传统的不带任何个人色彩的方形沙发区分开来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810082158196Kz9BGPLayq4H3CN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215818pmd1uGIK2tCPxBAS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810082158195wlUz9Fa41BtjA0b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215819ogcUL2SFQ1dY6sZe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215819lf58P4tpZTGh1X7n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215819ZGDLo7u0T23FbvNj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.693154\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://fritzhansen.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Republic of Fritz Hansen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Myro Deodorant by Visibility</h3><p>纽约设计工作室 Visibility 推出了一款极简主义风格的除臭剂 Myro Deodorant。设计团队从环保的角度出发，致力于创造一款尽可能少地使用塑料的产品，不仅易于使用，且要完全可回收且环保。</p><p>Myro Deodorant 设计的焦点集中在可重复使用的硬件外壳上，搭配可插入其中的可回收再填充盒，其使用的塑料比起药店常见的除臭剂少 50%。售价 10 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.mymyro.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215926bUOuzPHiZmSEIyW1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667200\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810082159261CfRXbwM6ElPQzdc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667200\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215927Qv4bEg16TjxZfnqW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667200\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810082159273q2glWdkiBDSsuRJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667200\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810082159285Orm3IQZAbEaxh8H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667200\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181008215926pJfr5ayQtYEU2Pxo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667200\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}